title: What We're Watching: 'Survivor: Cagayan'
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer, a 'Survivor' expert, and Craig Horlbeck, a 'Survivor' newbie, talk about 'Survivor: Cagayan' and what makes this season—and the franchise in general—so great.

Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Craig Horlbeck
